posting_body: ['Welcome to Valley Glen!!!', 'We are an Affordable Farm-Labor Community, as part of the qualification requirements, you must have income from agriculture, working directly with raw product, before the product has been processed.', '"At this time we are accepting applications to be placed on the waiting list ONLY".', 'Applications are available at our rental office: 1830 Gold Street Dixon, CA 95620', '"**RENTS DEPEND ON INCOME.', '**INCOME RESTRICTIONS APPLY".', 'We are conveniently located close to the library, across from the May Fair Grounds, City Park and shopping and restaurants.', 'Our beautiful property has great amenities including:', 'Energy Efficient Appliances and More', 'Energy Efficient Construction and Design', 'Dishwasher/Garbage Disposal', 'Refrigerator', 'Stove', 'Central Air Conditioning/Heating', 'Extra Storage Available', 'Two Car Garage', 'Community', 'On-Site Management', 'Community Room', 'Computer Room', 'Laundry Facility', 'Playground', 'On-Site Parking', '** Prices and availability might change without notice.', '"This institution is an Equal Opportunity Provider.', 'California Relay Service TDD', 'show contact info', '"']
